{"type": "article", "id": 40629, "title": "随时随地办公？这个小工作台满足你的需求｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-05-09T23:02:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 448, "name": "家具"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 1730, "name": "办公桌"}, {"id": 2559, "name": "花瓶"}, {"id": 6294, "name": "吊灯"}, {"id": 40270, "name": "锁"}, {"id": 40271, "name": "餐椅"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 141, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170509210335ghJo1eL9yRj42zaW.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「<b>BestDesign</b>」或是「<b>Qthings</b>」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Friday Lock by BIG &amp; Friday Labs</h3><p>智能家居产品越来越普及。最近，科技公司 Friday Labs 联手丹麦建筑事务所 BIG ，合作研发了一款智能锁 Friday Lock，在众筹平台 Indiegogo 众筹成功，自称是全球“最小最时尚”的智能锁。Friday Lock 造型简洁，适用于任何大门无需另做改装。它可以通过手机遥控开锁，当授权手机靠近大门时，会通过蓝牙自动解锁。若有人闯入，手机会通过应用程序发出警报，也可以远程解锁，让访客先行进入。目前，<a href=\"http://www.fridaylabs.net/views/home-page.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Friday Lock 已开放预售</a>，零售价为 249 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=m0501h76vvc&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210457S2m6C8JBekw7hZv0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.452865\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210457a8ZmgGyWeIXfjVxT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.542925\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210457wnxHhtk9Z61NWB3Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.823529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210458CpIEKHtWOFuowmBc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.533757\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210458siEUlChX3V96b1P5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.fridaylabs.net/views/home-page.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Friday Labs</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The PK1 Dining Chair by Poul Kjærholm</h3><p>丹麦家具制造商 Carl Hansen＆Son 最近重新投产了丹麦设计师 Poul Kjærholm 为其设计的第一把餐椅 PK1。这把餐椅最早发布于 1955 年，极简的钢架结构搭配拱形椅背，麻质绳索将椅座与椅背紧紧缠绕。更新版本的设计重新调整了餐椅的尺寸，以适应当代更高更大的人群。该品牌的首席执行官 <a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/05/07/carl-hansen-son-reissue-poul-kjaerholm-pk1-dining-chair-milan-design-week-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Knud Erik Hansen 表示</a>：“虽然 PK1 的细节非常简单，但它编织质感的座椅非常舒适，且贴合人的身体，在必要的地方可以给予身体完美支撑。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017050921061754oIXrMpbaqcBu9F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333756\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210617CJuwg6rBmItGVpOH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210619U8IfvymztPDX1rWw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.259306\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210620qUifmCJ0oxRlWbHz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.478849\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210620m4t3Gwo8Nre2ERlx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.582064\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210621WHiZBemb0PwaVho3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.408629\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/05/07/carl-hansen-son-reissue-poul-kjaerholm-pk1-dining-chair-milan-design-week-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>3D-printed Clay Vases by Olivier van Herpt</h3><p>近日，时尚品牌 COS 联手毕业于埃因霍温设计学院的荷兰设计师 Olivier van Herpt，推出了一系列 3D 打印花瓶，展示于 COS 位于伦敦摄政街的店铺中。这一系列花瓶的设计灵感源自 COS 今年的夏季新品，尤其是注意到了面料的颜色和纹理，赋予花瓶轻柔曲线的外观。而用粘土作为打印材质，使得花瓶的表面远观显得尤为光滑，近看又带着细微的纹理。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210723yWp1l3ObaL4zxYZk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210726rjHmbRTIdUugx526.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.483926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210727BZsfW1mTQGYRjU3e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.472504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210756CS4VAjZfH7rLQN9O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.347293\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/05/06/cos-x-olivier-van-herpt-3d-printed-clay-vases-homeware-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>PRAN LAMPS by Position Collective</h3><p>PRAN 系列吊灯出自匈牙利设计团体 Position Collective。这一系列的设计灵感源自一趟印度之旅，不管是大地色调还是纹理的设计。铜材、黄铜和钢材的叠加使用很妙，压制金属和塑料部分的不同组合，可以为 PRAN 系列带来 50 种不同的轮廓变化，创造独特的灯型。售价 126 至 329 英镑不等，<a href=\"https://clippings.com/search?query=PRAN\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017050921084632yvC7QpuU6LYPHh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210846EVbc7TPZkpQW6B8o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639054\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210846PRoKwzfQr7CvJ1Yi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639119\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210847Z5RBdHYc2egTklmt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639054\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210851qQuMyFJT8Y7ma4eo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639054\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509210853Hb7ZlS61u4jFKzGY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639054\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://position-collective.com/portfolio/pran-lamps/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Position Collective</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>DeskView by MINIMAL</h3><p>入职一家新公司，如果有选择的可能，你是否会优先考虑选一处位于窗边的工位，好在工作之余一览窗外风景。芝加哥设计公司 MINIMAL 最近就推出了一款名为“ DeskView ”的办公桌，不再局限于传统办公桌的样式，它小巧的结构，可以吸附于玻璃等任何光滑垂直的表面，办公桌的面积恰好能够放得下一台笔记本电脑或是书和笔记本，同时也能满足不少为健康着想的办公一族站立式办公的需求。售价 165 美元，<a href=\"http://shopdeskview.com/product/deskview/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=i0501gswlbp&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705092110292Z4cEdt8TjrpCPJK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.741406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509211029iMVtLrozCG4IsWP6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509211029RvFeudlVSG8M7jpf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509211030whCvFS2e6MJkL39x.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705092110292OXuqVDwzdsHA1ml.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://shopdeskview.com/product/deskview/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Deskview</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Flexible, Movable Furniture by CL3 and Lim + Lu </h3><p>香港 CL3 设计公司联手纽约设计公司 Lim + Lu 推出的这套灵活、可移动的家具系列，很容易让人联想到那些搬运车和拌匀工人用来运输重型箱子和家具的手推车。这一系列的每一件家具，既可以用作固定位置摆放的家具，亦可作为可移动的推车，将其推移至任何位置。可躺，可坐，可置物，可移动，可储物，总之，如果使用者想象力足够，就可以把这一系列的家具玩出很多花样，尤其是在户外，更可以一展身手，尝试多种玩法。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509211132Xi7hp425yTRfbePl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509211132Fu87PfWjD5UtvHrS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705092111340FMEfhUdKP4gAbCO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509211135bsURFPTqEpcALQm4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705092111365qvtpQ2U9kDfO7bF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500781\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170509211136iBeSCkQEyjFxbL1g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500781\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://design-milk.com/flexible-movable-furniture-inspired-by-hand-trucks/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designmilk</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}